# i18n GUI Alignment

- Always use the app i18n mechanism for user-facing GUI text.
- Do not hardcode visible UI strings in layout/components; use translation keys and `t(...)`.
- When introducing or changing GUI text, update locale bundles in `frontend/data/i18n/` in the same change.
- Keep locale key sets aligned across `en`, `de`, `fr`, `it`, and `es`.
- Preserve hybrid policy:
  - UI strings in per-language i18n files.
  - Domain vocabularies (for example ECO names) as side-by-side multilingual domain data.
